### Week 5 - Ask with new session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "question": "What is the main content of this knowledge base?",
  "topK": 5
}


### Week 5 - Ask with existing session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "sessionId": 1,
  "question": "Can you explain it in more detail?",
  "topK": 5
}


### Week 5 - List sessions by spaceId
GET http://localhost:8080/api/qa/history/spaces/1/sessions


### Week 5 - List messages by sessionId
GET http://localhost:8080/api/qa/history/sessions/1/messages


### Week 5 - List references by assistant messageId
GET http://localhost:8080/api/qa/history/messages/2/references


### Week 5 - Get full session history
GET http://localhost:8080/api/qa/history/sessions/1